Bob The Robber is a stealth-action game where you play as Bob, a clever thief sneaking through buildings to steal valuables without getting caught. Use your skills to avoid guards, disable alarms, and grab the loot!

🕵️‍♂️ Objective: Complete heists by stealing items and escaping safely.
🎮 How to Play: Sneak, hide, and use gadgets to outsmart security.
⚠️ Tip: Timing and stealth are key—stay in the shadows!

Experience exciting stealth gameplay and clever puzzles with Bob The Robber!

